'''米增戈·卡扬扎·彼得·平达'''（'''Mizengo Kayanza Peter Pinda'''；{{bd|1948年|8月12日|||}}) [[坦桑尼亚|坦桑尼亚]][[坦桑尼亚革命党|坦桑尼亚革命党(CCM)]]政治家，2005年成为[[卡塔维区|卡塔维]]地区议员，2008年担任[[坦桑尼亚总理|坦桑尼亚总理]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.parliament.go.tz/index.php/members/mpcvs/1038/minister|title=Member of Parliament CV|date=|work=|publisher=[[Parliament_of_Tanzania|Parliament of Tanzania]]|accessdate=6 September 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140701140339/http://parliament.go.tz/index.php/members/mpcvs/1038/minister|archivedate=2014年7月1日}}</ref>

==生平==
平达出生于坦桑尼亚西部地区[[鲁夸区|鲁夸区]]。<ref name=APA>[http://apanews.net/apa.php?page=show_article_eng&id_article=54501 "Mizengo Kayanza Peter Pinda becomes new Tanzanian premier"] {{webarchive|url=http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/20080214042015/http://apanews.net/apa.php?page=show_article_eng&id_article=54501 |date=2008-02-14 }}, African Press Agency, February 8, 2008.</ref>1974年获得[[达累斯萨拉姆大学|达累斯萨拉姆大学]]法律学位。<ref name=APA/><ref name=New>Angel Navuri, [http://www.ippmedia.com/ipp/guardian/2008/02/09/108033.html "The new premier"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081119083433/http://ippmedia.com/ipp/guardian/2008/02/09/108033.html |date=2008-11-19 }}, ''Guardian'' (IPP Media), February 9, 2008.</ref>

1982年至1992年他担任总统助理私人秘书，1996年至2000年是内阁书记。此后在2000年当选议员，并进入总理府担任总理办公室副主任，分管地区行政和地方政府。<ref name=New/>2006年被提升为部长级主任。<ref>Hassan Muhiddin, [http://www.ippmedia.com/ipp/guardian/2006/01/05/57238.html "JK’s beefed up team"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ippmedia.com/ipp/guardian/2006/01/05/57238.html |date=20070103223211 }}, ''Guardian'' (IPP Media), January 5, 2006.</ref>

[[File:Hillary_Clinton_and_Mizengo_Pinda.jpg|thumb]]]]
2008年2月8日，在[[爱德华·洛瓦萨|爱德华·洛瓦萨]]总理因腐败指控辞职后，平达被总统[[贾卡亚·基奎特|贾卡亚·基奎特]]提名为总理，同日在议会中获得279票赞成，两票反对，一票弃权，通过任命，<ref>[http://www.ippmedia.com/ipp/guardian/2008/02/09/108034.html "It is Pinda"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080820110522/http://ippmedia.com/ipp/guardian/2008/02/09/108034.html |date=2008-08-20 }}, ''Guardian'' (IPP Media), February 9, 2008.</ref>2月9日正式就职。<ref>Bilham Kimati and Angel Navuri, [http://www.ippmedia.com/ipp/observer/2008/02/10/108085.html "Pinda sworn-in as PM"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080719165711/http://ippmedia.com/ipp/observer/2008/02/10/108085.html |date=2008-07-19 }}, ''Sunday Observer'' (IPP Media), February 10, 2008.</ref>平达政府削减政府规模，将29个部长缩减为26个，31个副部长减少到21个。<ref>[http://www.ippmedia.com/ipp/guardian/2008/02/13/108291.html "JK trims cabinet size"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ippmedia.com/ipp/guardian/2008/02/13/108291.html |date=20080420083252 }}, ''Guardian'' (IPP Media), February 13, 2008.</ref>


